# Stoic AF - Environment Variables
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your actual values.
# DO NOT commit .env.local to git - it contains sensitive credentials
# This file is safe to commit as it contains only placeholder values

# ============================================================================
# FRONTEND ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES (Vite)
# These are exposed in the browser, so use PUBLIC keys only
# ============================================================================

# Supabase API URL
# Local example: http://supa.stoicaf.local or http://192.168.4.219:8000
